Description: Remote connection manager (SSH, RDP, VNC, FTP, SFTP)
 OrbitalTerm is a desktop remote-connection manager. It organizes and opens
 SSH, RDP, VNC, FTP, SFTP and embedded-browser sessions from a single tabbed
 workspace, with folders, data sources and quick search.
 .
 Saved passwords are encrypted at rest (AES-256-GCM) and all data is stored
 locally — no accounts, no cloud.
